<P>
<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Fromson, &quot;Wealthy Scramble for Tax
Avoidance Strategies.&quot;
<P>
<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Robert Lenzner and Phillipe Mao, &quot;The
New Refugees,&quot; <I>Forbes</I>, November 21, 1994.
<P>
<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;George F. Will, &quot;Making Capitalism
