<P>
<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For a detailed discussion of the role
of capital in the economy, see Daniel J. Mitchell, &quot;An Action
Plan to Create Jobs,&quot; Heritage Foundation <I>Memo to President&#173;Elect
Clinton</I> No. 1, December 14, 1992. See also Gary Robbins and
