http://www.cpac.org:80/wash_times/campaign.4_28.html 204.71.237.74 19970108210251 text/html 3564
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 21:02:58 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 22-Apr-96 09:22:26 GMT
