http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/library/categories/natsec/bg1074.html 204.71.237.74 19970108213447 text/html 46260
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 21:34:50 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 20-Mar-96 14:48:52 GMT
