83, December 29, 1995.
<li>Safire, "Stop the Giveaway."
<li>Peter C. Cramton, "Money Out of Thin Air: The Nationwide Narrowband PCS Auction," 
<i>Journal of Economics and Management Strategy</i>, Vol. 4, No. 2 (Summer 1995), p. 339.
<li><i>Ibid</i>.
</ol><p>
<p>
