http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/p_review/jan96/meese.html 204.71.237.74 19970108224105 text/html 27726
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 22:41:12 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jan-96 22:41:16 GMT
